Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EN,,0,0,0,,--------------------TEXT-EN--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.19,0:00:01.61,EN,,0,0,0,,What’s your name, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:02.48,EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, I’m Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.52,EN,,0,0,0,,I teach middle school band
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:05.92,EN,,0,0,0,,Connie, got to go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.20,EN,,0,0,0,,I play this jazz teacher who’s sort of stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:16.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, happily stuck, but still stuck in a job where he’s teaching jazz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:21.33,EN,,0,0,0,,which is a sort of a throwback of trade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.44,EN,,0,0,0,,and when it comes to musical trade, he’s teaching jazz to his
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:27.42,EN,,0,0,0,,to his little, you know, his little kids in school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:31.34,EN,,0,0,0,,But Joe has always dreamed of being something else
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.84,EN,,0,0,0,,In his heart, he’s a musician at heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:37.17,EN,,0,0,0,,and since he was very young Joe always wanted to be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.54,EN,,0,0,0,,a professional jazz musician
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.37,EN,,0,0,0,,You could say that jazz music is the dream that Joe’s been pursuing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:44.81,EN,,0,0,0,,on nights and weekends, his entire adult life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:47.01,EN,,0,0,0,,This is big gig that’s coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.56,EN,,0,0,0,,and he wants to go play for it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:53.63,EN,,0,0,0,,He finally goes and auditions and he get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:56.66,EN,,0,0,0,,and for musicians or anybody out there when you get lost in your craft
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:59.95,EN,,0,0,0,,He’s just in his thing auditioning no nerves he went
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.47,EN,,0,0,0,,and they said wow you’re great
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.91,EN,,0,0,0,,you will have the gig
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:08.17,EN,,0,0,0,,And then has an accident that causes his soul to leave his body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.34,EN,,0,0,0,,and almost go to the Great Beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:14.84,EN,,0,0,0,,And so, he is trying to get back into his body and back to his life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:18.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Is this heaven? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:22.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Is it H.E. Double Hockey sticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.01,EN,,0,0,0,,hell…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:29.51,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s easy to get turned around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:32.30,EN,,0,0,0,,This isn’t the Great Beyond, it’s the Great Before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:33.91,EN,,0,0,0,,The Great Before?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:35.74,EN,,0,0,0,,I played a character named 22
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.81,EN,,0,0,0,,who is a soul that’s never been born
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.68,EN,,0,0,0,,because even though the people in the Great Before
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:42.74,EN,,0,0,0,,have been trying to convince her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.28,EN,,0,0,0,,She had a lot of mentors trying to convince her that life is great
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:46.64,EN,,0,0,0,,and she should go live on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.82,EN,,0,0,0,,She is very suspect of it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:52.28,EN,,0,0,0,,she thinks it sounds scary, painful, difficult, depressing, smelly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.55,EN,,0,0,0,,She just doesn’t want any part of it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.50,EN,,0,0,0,,She is a Joe’s chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:57.53,EN,,0,0,0,,if he can kind of convince her to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.76,EN,,0,0,0,,then maybe he’ll get a chance to go back also
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:10.71,EN,,0,0,0,,Initially I think that character’s name was 107,337,217,322
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.42,EN,,0,0,0,,we called her 22 for short
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.18,EN,,0,0,0,,But in the end we decided it’s actually funnier if she is just 22
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.53,EN,,0,0,0,,That’s how long she’s been up there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.97,EN,,0,0,0,,and she still wants nothing to do with earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:25.63,EN,,0,0,0,,You know, we thought of her a little bit, 22 is kind of like a teenager
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:27.61,EN,,0,0,0,,who thinks they know everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:31.25,EN,,0,0,0,,In 22’s case, she can make a pretty compelling argument that she does
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.49,EN,,0,0,0,,because she’s been looking down on earth and taking notes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:36.26,EN,,0,0,0,,for a long, long, long time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:41.26,EN,,0,0,0,,and to her it looks like a lot of suffering and disappointment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.30,EN,,0,0,0,,and why, why get mixed up in that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.77,EN,,0,0,0,,22 is a, I would say lack of a better word, not cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.44,EN,,0,0,0,,but it’s like doesn’t really see the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:55.39,EN,,0,0,0,,She’s been there, quite literally, thousands of years and refuses to go to earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:59.38,EN,,0,0,0,,She cannot get a ticket; she cannot get her earth badge to change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Because she thinks that there’s nothing good about going to earth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.35,EN,,0,0,0,,So, we have the situation where we have a soul
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.14,EN,,0,0,0,,who doesn’t want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.83,EN,,0,0,0,,being stuck with a soul who doesn’t want to live
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.72,EN,,0,0,0,,22 has been at the You Seminar for quite some time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:18.00,EN,,0,0,0,,and has had such notable mentors as Gandhi, Abraham Lincoln, and Mother Teresa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.61,EN,,0,0,0,,I made her cry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:20.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Ignore that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.63,EN,,0,0,0,,you got the talented Tina Fey
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.61,EN,,0,0,0,,who’s just, you know I mean, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:26.59,EN,,0,0,0,,That her mind and the way she works is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.51,EN,,0,0,0,,Plus, she’s a writer as well you know she started out as a writer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.85,EN,,0,0,0,,and you know being on Saturday night live so just to be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.22,EN,,0,0,0,,sort of go back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.28,EN,,0,0,0,,even when we weren’t in the same room with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:37.94,EN,,0,0,0,,He was only in the same room a couple of times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.15,EN,,0,0,0,,But just being in her presence man made everything you know, elevated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.87,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I read her biography and she said she spent a lot of her youth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:49.24,EN,,0,0,0,,standing on the sidelines with the “cool kids”, making fun of people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.73,EN,,0,0,0,,And I think in a way that really personifies 22
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:57.38,EN,,0,0,0,,She’s, she doesn’t want to get involved with all these messiness and drama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.34,EN,,0,0,0,,She wants to be on the side, just judging
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.45,EN,,0,0,0,,Jamie Foxx plays Joe Gardner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.80,EN,,0,0,0,,and he’s incredible in the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.22,EN,,0,0,0,,because one, he’s a really great actor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.77,EN,,0,0,0,,but also because he is a musician himself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:13.10,EN,,0,0,0,,All the parts of Joe’s character that are tied to his love of music
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.27,EN,,0,0,0,,just feel really authentic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.31,EN,,0,0,0,,and connected coming from Jamie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.23,EN,,0,0,0,,and he’s just super expressive with his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:23.55,EN,,0,0,0,,Guy can do everything; you know he’s great dramatic actor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.11,EN,,0,0,0,,he’s got comedy chops, he loves music, he understands music
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:32.34,EN,,0,0,0,,He’s a great musician himself and he has this unrelenting optimism and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:37.50,EN,,0,0,0,,that I think all of which were essential for really bringing Joe to the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.00,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s almost as if there was a computer program
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.51,EN,,0,0,0,,where you wanted to feed all these traits into the program
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.19,EN,,0,0,0,,and ask for like, OK,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:47.23,EN,,0,0,0,,feed all the traits for the prefect person to play Joe Gardner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.85,EN,,0,0,0,,It would spit out Jamie Foxx
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.29,EN,,0,0,0,,This is the guy I was telling you about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.82,EN,,0,0,0,,my old middle school band teacher, Mr. Gardener
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.20,EN,,0,0,0,,Call me Joe, Dorothea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:59.73,EN,,0,0,0,,I mean Mrs. Williams, it’s a pleasure, wow this is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.53,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, Joe is, Oh gosh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.45,EN,,0,0,0,,He is so enamored of Dorothea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.53,EN,,0,0,0,,he recognizes what a great musician she is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.59,EN,,0,0,0,,He recognizes the opportunity that’s before him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.41,EN,,0,0,0,,He knows he better not to mess up that this may be a one-time thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.88,EN,,0,0,0,,that this was a gift that literally landed in his lap
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.43,EN,,0,0,0,,that sort of was orchestrated from years previous
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:25.06,EN,,0,0,0,,because he, Joe, was actually the mentor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:28.46,EN,,0,0,0,,the middle school teacher of this drummer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.27,EN,,0,0,0,,One of the students who’s a drummer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:35.62,EN,,0,0,0,,who, because of his artistry and wound up it Dorothea’s band
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:38.47,EN,,0,0,0,,and this particular day, someone falls out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:41.40,EN,,0,0,0,,and it’s time for the understudy to go on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.03,EN,,0,0,0,,What I enjoyed about what Jamie Foxx
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.24,EN,,0,0,0,,brought to the role of Joe Garden was that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:50.04,EN,,0,0,0,,there’s a space that musicians often get in that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.83,EN,,0,0,0,,mere mortals don’t tend to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.73,EN,,0,0,0,,and that’s when you get into a zone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.54,EN,,0,0,0,,people tend to tag it as like, musician’s face
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.29,EN,,0,0,0,,You know, whenever your eyes are closed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.64,EN,,0,0,0,,and you’re making these wired faces
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.78,EN,,0,0,0,,that’s sort of a spiritual experience
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.87,EN,,0,0,0,,You know, that’s where you get into the zone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:13.42,EN,,0,0,0,,and I love the fact that Jamie’s character often gets to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.72,EN,,0,0,0,,go to that place and explain to people why us musicians
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.01,EN,,0,0,0,,go to that place, where, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.46,EN,,0,0,0,,we make these wired faces, and our eyes are closed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:27.40,EN,,0,0,0,,We’re going to a place another dimension unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:30.66,EN,,0,0,0,,Only known to other creatives and that’s the zone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.76,EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry I zoned out a little back there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.33,EN,,0,0,0,,Joe Gardener, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.07,EN,,0,0,0,,I’ve been, uh, teaching middle school band
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.59,EN,,0,0,0,,But on the weekends, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.43,EN,,0,0,0,,You got a suit? Get a suit, teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.48,EN,,0,0,0,,A good suit, back here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:54.09,EN,,0,0,0,,First shows at nine, sound checks at seven
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.68,EN,,0,0,0,,We’ll see how you do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.39,EN,,0,0,0,,The first writer I work with was Mike Jones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:05.42,EN,,0,0,0,,Mike and I crafted the world and the basic bones of the story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.57,EN,,0,0,0,,But as we run into the specificity of Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.81,EN,,0,0,0,,and wanting to know more about this character
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:14.11,EN,,0,0,0,,We realized, though, we need somebody who has more to bring
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.95,EN,,0,0,0,,from this background and Kemp,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.03,EN,,0,0,0,,not only a great writer, but he ended up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.20,EN,,0,0,0,,stepping in so many different ways
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:26.71,EN,,0,0,0,,in regard to set design what kind of posters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.26,EN,,0,0,0,,will be at Joe’s house or mom’s house
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:33.26,EN,,0,0,0,,and Queens, you know, the authenticity of the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.09,EN,,0,0,0,,Of course, Joe and his passions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:39.97,EN,,0,0,0,,and what kind of music he listens to and all this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.02,EN,,0,0,0,,we ended up making Kemp co-director
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.16,EN,,0,0,0,,because he just, was bringing so much to almost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:49.94,EN,,0,0,0,,every department and I think it really ups the whole film
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.45,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s the incredible Pixar, you know I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.58,EN,,0,0,0,,the way they think 4 or 5,6 dimension you know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.37,EN,,0,0,0,,that’s I mean you think about it the movies that have come before
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.04,EN,,0,0,0,,when I deal with these types of subject matters are really
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.04,EN,,0,0,0,,really opened up different sides of your head
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.40,EN,,0,0,0,,What the movie is telling us and actually what Joe learns
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:13.68,EN,,0,0,0,,is that there is more to living life than achievement
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:18.46,EN,,0,0,0,,which is a really interesting thing to try to take in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.37,EN,,0,0,0,,You know, there’s just being present and being in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.26,EN,,0,0,0,,and making connections and having feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.75,EN,,0,0,0,,there’s more to life than checking boxes of things
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.36,EN,,0,0,0,,you’ve wanted to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.13,EN,,0,0,0,,Jamie you know Jamie is just too quick with it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:34.00,EN,,0,0,0,,and he’s so fast on his feet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:38.43,EN,,0,0,0,,so he has brought a lot of character, a lot of warmth to Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.37,EN,,0,0,0,,and in the course of the story, this, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:46.19,EN,,0,0,0,,different characters take over different bodies and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:52.11,EN,,0,0,0,,but you just enjoy following Jamie in all his machinations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.67,EN,,0,0,0,,in whatever way he shows up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.11,EN,,0,0,0,,We can’t taste it either?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.72,EN,,0,0,0,,All that stuff is in your body
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.35,EN,,0,0,0,,No smell, no taste, or touch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.39,EN,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.36,EN,,0,0,0,,OK, I got it
